comments: Solid basis for corporate finance topics

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: Very informative but the three hour lecture style lends itself to the student tuning out towards the end of the lectures

Strengths: great slides and course organization. Problem sets are well-designs for consolidate understanding of course material, and the exams are fair.

Weaknesses: can cover topics more in depth or include a final project of actually valuing a company

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: If youre going into business of any kind this class is fundamental
Yes, you learn a lot about corporate Finance without being drowned in work. Professor Kelly Shue explains concepts very clearly.
